  "text": "We define AB and AV AR following respectively (46) and (47) in [CITATION_1] ] (Section 5, p. 28). Note that AB and AV AR are already of the right asymptotic order in the sense that α −1 AB → P AB and α −2 AV AR → P T 0 (AV s ) 1/2 dB s (see (48) and (49) in Corollary 4 of the cited paper). We provide now the studentized version of (4.15).",
